  <acronym>RESPONSIBLE</acronym>
  <official_title>Effect on Exercise Capacity of Fixed Rate Vs Rate RESPONSIve Pacing in Patients With Permanent AF and Left Ventricular Dysfunction Underwent Radiofrequency Atrioventricular Junction aBLation and bivEntricular Pacing (RESPONSIBLE Study)</official_title>
